Connection conn=DriverManager.getConnection("jdbc:mariadb://localhost:3306/db useSSH=false","root","123");

this is jdbc mariadb.jar file for established connection between mysql-server and mysql-client

https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.mariadb.jdbc/mariadb-java-client/3.2.0



